captions.text:
Dani, Andy and Edu
will play "Quick Change".

How does it work?
Every time I say 'change',

they have to change the last
thing they have said or done.

I can say 'more' and they have to go
bigger, or 'less' and they go smaller.

I'll pick up a sentence to be the title
of the scene, and the sentence is:

'I don't get paid quickly,
so I don't work in a hurry'

It's "Quick Change",
starting now!
Change!
Change!
Dammit!
Júnior!
What...

I'm calling you to my desk,
can you come here please?

- I just needed one more...
- Needed what? Come here.

This is exactly what
I want to talk about!
Change!
Change!

- This is exactly what I want
to talk about! - Yes, sir.

- I have two reports for tomorrow
and I asked you... - More!

- I asked for you to deliver
today three reports... - More!

Where's the fuckin' report
due yesterday?

Everything's urgent for you! I don't get
paid quickly, so I don't work in a hurry!

- Listen, I pay you to work...
- Change!

- Look, my mother pays you
to obey me... - Change!

- I don't pay you, but we made a
deal to work for free... - Change!

If I'm sleeping with you...
I need to get something in return!
Or else I'll tell everyone in the office!

- Did you know?
- What happened?

- The boss is sleeping with an employee!
- No way!
And he thinks nobody knows!

- Look, they have some pictures
in Facebook! - More!

- Look, they have an album
in Facebook! - More!

- There's an Youtube channel
with all of their videos! - More!

There's a website, bossemployee.com.br
with a complete dossier!
Wow, I'm gonna share!

- Share, share, share...
- Share, share, share...
Poke, share...

I just got this via Whatsapp...
Why did you do this?
You used to be gentler...
I slap you because you ask for it!

Look, it's on TMZ!
'Boss likes to get spanked'!
At Beverly Hills!
I guess we're done.
Yes, we have done it a lot!

Look, it's on TMZ!
'Employee says they did it'!
At Beverly Hills!

I called you all here
because of those rumors...

- What rumors, boss?
- I don't know anything!

- We just got here...
- Change!

- Rumors? Everybody...
- Change!

- We dig it.
- Yeah, we know...
It's on my Whatsapp all day long!

We have a group just for
the stuff we find about you!

- It's non-stop. 350 messages per hour...
- My battery can't handle it!

- I had to disable the notifications,
I couldn't work! - Can't work!
The videos? Jeez!

- They keep coming, one after another...
- All right, thanks!
I'd like to know your opinion!

- I think you make a very sweet couple!
- I think it's a horror!
More!

I think you're the most
cuddly-wuddly couple!

- I think it's disgusting!
- More!
Cute, cute, cute!
May Jesus free you from this disease!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented
